N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 160.7 - Effect of Rules

State Regulations

The rules set forth in this Part shall not supersede any
existing rule or order of the Chief Judge of the State or of the Chief

Administrative Judge, or any provision of statute, including but not limited to
section 4547 of the CPLR and Article 21-A of the Judiciary
